{"tid":588101,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"蘭拓的A7M3測試出來了 - 劇情果然有反轉","createTime":"2018-03-11T03:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T02:36:22.000Z","uid":107023,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9970a519d0957e4f29917a95b3d2033954930c","tid":588101,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.irentals.cn/#/articles/215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irentals.cn%2F%23%2Farticles%2F215&d=Zi3dU1milWSUjNvnFpVMMgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f7590d3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.irentals.cn/#/articles/215</a><br />\n<br />\n1.A7M3確認有低通；<br />\n<br />\n2.A7M3動態範圍持平A7R3，不如縮圖後的A7R3；<br />\n<br />\n3.A7M3的容寬度略低於A​​7R3；<br />\n<br />\n4.A7M3的高感畫質在iso3200之前不如縮圖後的A7R3；超過3200之後和縮圖後的A7R3差不多；<br />\n<br />\n5.A7M3的追焦能力（傳感器刷新率和追焦成功率）略強於A7R3，遠不如A9<br />\n<br />\n無反的追焦好壞和cmos的刷新率有關，a7r3是13fps，a7m3是20fps，a9是160fps(但因cpu 限制只做到每秒60次af/ae 計算)，都和a9差距很大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從成像質量來說，A7m3的CMOS就是A7R3成像芯片的降像素版本，同代技術，讀取速度也是差不多的。 A7r3縮圖會因為超採樣有點優勢"},{"pid":"5344f86366f626c20ae939ef1e1548c9c73b4cb8","tid":588101,"uid":40445,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:48:31.000Z","msg":"劇情反轉咗啲乜?"},{"pid":"4bdeffca767b0697e3d43def12b31b8054153a54","tid":588101,"uid":28001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5344f86366f626c20ae939ef1e1548c9c73b4cb8","tid":588101,"uid":40445,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:48:31.000Z","msg":"劇情反轉咗啲乜?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:59:52.000Z","msg":"係囉。。呢啲唔係一早預左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02bc98cf7027c961638212bd57ca15e5915a5df","tid":588101,"uid":16986,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"攞另外兩部機嘅最大賣點黎比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nA7III砌低A9追焦+A7III畫質就劇情反轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\"